    <note type="biography">
        <p>Writer on household management and journalist. Née Isabella Mary Mayson. Educated at Islington and Heidelberg. Married Samuel Orchart Beeton, publisher and editor, in 1856. Author of <hi rend="italic">Mrs Beeton’s book of household management</hi> (1859–61) and editor of the <hi rend="italic">English Woman’s Domestic Magazine.</hi></p></note>
